A PUPPY ONCE WITH MY CAR.

23:04.250 --> 23:06.419
I ONLY HAD
MY LEARNER'S PERMIT.

23:12.825 --> 23:15.728
- Doctor: 24 YEARS OLD?
- Hannah: MM-HMM.

