THE NURSE WEIGHED ME
WITH CLOTHES ON,

23:21.233 --> 23:24.036
SO THAT WAS
A RUDE THING TO DO.

23:24.136 --> 23:25.705
SEXUALLY ACTIVE?

23:25.805 --> 23:28.541
- JUST ONE PARTNER OR...?
- SHOULD I GET MORE?

23:28.641 --> 23:31.444
BECAUSE THE ONE I'VE GOT
IS KIND OF A HANDFUL.

23:33.279 --> 23:34.413
YEAH, IT'S JUST HIM.

23:34.514 --> 23:37.617
AND DO YOU USE
PROTECTION? CONDOMS?

23:37.717 --> 23:40.520
I ALWAYS USE CONDOMS,
BUT I'VE BEEN THINKING
A LOT LATELY

23:40.620 --> 23:42.722
ABOUT THE STUFF THAT GETS UP
AROUND THE SIDES OF CONDOMS.

23:42.822 --> 23:45.057
WHAT IS THE DEAL
WITH ALL OF THAT STUFF,
YOU KNOW?

23:46.425 --> 23:48.394
YOU MEAN... THE SEMEN?

23:48.495 --> 23:49.762
I MEAN, ALL OF IT.

23:49.862 --> 23:51.831
I HAVE A VERY BAD
FEAR OF AIDS.

23:51.931 --> 23:53.533
HAVE YOU KNOWN
SOMEONE WITH AIDS?

23:53.633 --> 23:55.902
IT'S MORE OF LIKE
A "FORREST GUMP"-BASED FEAR.

23:56.002 --> 23:59.438
THAT'S WHAT
ROBIN WRIGHT PENN'S
CHARACTER DIED OF.

24:00.439 --> 24:02.475
OKAY, JUST LIE BACK
FOR ME, OKAY?

24:02.575 --> 24:04.310
YEAH. JUST...

24:04.410 --> 24:05.912
- YES, LEGS UP.
- MM-HMM.

24:06.012 --> 24:08.014
YEAH.
OH, OKAY.

24:08.114 --> 24:10.116
PERFECT, THANK YOU.

24:12.519 --> 24:14.954
THE THING IS THAT
THESE DAYS IF YOU ARE
DIAGNOSED WITH AIDS,

24:15.054 --> 24:16.823
YOU KNOW, IT'S ACTUALLY--
IT'S NOT A DEATH SENTENCE.

24:16.923 --> 24:20.660
THERE'S SO MANY GOOD DRUGS
AND PEOPLE LIVE A LONG TIME.

24:22.529 --> 24:24.731
ALSO, YOU KNOW,
IF YOU HAVE AIDS,

24:24.831 --> 24:26.899
THERE'S A LOT OF STUFF
PEOPLE AREN'T GONNA
BOTHER YOU ABOUT,

24:26.999 --> 24:29.101
