NO ONE'S GONNA CALL YOU
ON THE PHONE AND SAY,

24:29.201 --> 24:31.137
"DID YOU GET A JOB?"
OR "DID YOU PAY YOUR RENT?"

24:31.237 --> 24:32.572
OR "ARE YOU TAKING
AN HTML COURSE?"

24:32.672 --> 24:34.373
BECAUSE ALL THEY'RE
GONNA SAY IS, LIKE,

24:34.473 --> 24:38.044
"CONGRATULATIONS
ON NOT BEING DEAD."

24:38.144 --> 24:40.312
AND IT'S ALSO
A REALLY GOOD EXCUSE
TO BE MAD AT A GUY.

24:40.412 --> 24:42.314
IT'S NOT JUST
SOMETHING DUMB LIKE,
"YOU DIDN'T TEXT ME."

24:42.414 --> 24:43.616
IT'S LIKE,
"YOU GAVE ME AIDS,

24:43.716 --> 24:48.020
SO DEAL WITH THAT...
FOREVER."

24:48.120 --> 24:50.790
MAYBE I ACTUALLY
AM NOT SCARED OF AIDS.

24:50.890 --> 24:52.424
