I WAS SCARED OF AIDS,

24:52.525 --> 24:56.929
AND WHAT I REALLY AM
IS WANTING AIDS.

25:01.901 --> 25:05.337
THAT IS AN INCREDIBLY
SILLY THING TO SAY.

25:05.437 --> 25:06.839
YOU DO NOT WANT AIDS.

25:06.939 --> 25:09.776
DO YOU KNOW THAT
EVERY 35 MINUTES

